      <title>87 岁的挪威国王哈拉尔将永久减少活动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norways-king-harald-87-permanently-scale-back-activity-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[王室周一表示，87 岁的挪威国王哈拉尔将永久减少他参加的官方活动数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norways-king-harald-87-permanently-scale-back-activity-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:42:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于进口萎缩，印尼3月份贸易顺差超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-posts-larger-than-expected-trade-surplus-march-imports-shrink-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[统计局周一公布的数据显示，印尼3月份贸易顺差为44.7亿美元，高于路透社调查中预测的11.3亿美元顺差，原因是进口降幅超过预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-posts-larger-than-expected-trade-surplus-march-imports-shrink-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:53:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡3月份通胀率降至2.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lankas-inflation-drops-25-march-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一官方数据显示，斯里兰卡 3 月份消费者价格通胀率从 2 月份的 5.1% 降至 2.5%，因为为实现国际货币基金组织 29 亿美元计划设定的目标而提高销售税的影响逐渐消退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lankas-inflation-drops-25-march-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:40:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾东部县发生地震</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-eastern-county-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾气象局称，台湾东部花莲县周一发生 5.5 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-eastern-county-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾3月出口订单低于预期，但政府寄希望于人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-march-export-orders-trails-forecasts-govt-pins-hopes-ai-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾3月份出口订单增幅低于预期，但政府表示，预计人工智能（AI）应用需求的激增将推动台湾高科技产品的未来需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-march-export-orders-trails-forecasts-govt-pins-hopes-ai-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国反对日本首相参拜靖国神社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周一对日本首相岸田文雄在东京一座有争议的神社举行祭祀活动表示强烈反对，中国和韩国认为该神社是日本昔日军事侵略的象征。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国梦的破灭迫使西方金融公司削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在几年前，中国经济蓬勃发展带来的利润丰厚的商业前景导致西方金融公司（从投资银行到资产管理）竞相扩大业务范围并从世界各地招募人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统抵达巴基斯坦进行为期三天的访问以修复关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/iranian-president-lands-pakistan-three-day-visit-mend-ties-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部表示，在巴基斯坦首都戒备森严的情况下，伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西周一抵达伊斯兰堡，开始为期三天的正式访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/iranian-president-lands-pakistan-three-day-visit-mend-ties-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称朝鲜人可能帮助创作了西方漫画</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreans-may-have-helped-create-western-cartoons-report-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份研究报告发现，尽管国际社会对朝鲜实施了制裁，朝鲜动画师可能还是帮助亚马逊和 HBO Max 等西方大公司创作了受欢迎的电视动画片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreans-may-have-helped-create-western-cartoons-report-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚法院驳回选举争议，维持当选总统普拉博沃的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-court-rejects-first-two-petitions-seeking-election-re-run-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚一家法院周一驳回了两名落败候选人寻求重新参加二月总统选举的挑战，并驳回了取消获胜者普拉博沃·苏比安托及其竞选伙伴资格的请求，结束了所有选举纠纷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-court-rejects-first-two-petitions-seeking-election-re-run-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:52:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
